            <title><![CDATA[PS5's High Price Is Impacting Monster Hunter Wilds Sales, Capcom Exec Says]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5s-high-price-is-impacting-monster-hunter-wilds-sales-capcom-exec-says/1100-6534430/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
